  <summary date="2023-08-09T18:17:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Saving Abortion Facilities from Extremists for Patients Act or the SAFE for Patients Act 

This bill establishes a civil action for damaging or destroying a reproductive health care facility or for harassing, injuring, or intimidating a person who provides or obtains reproductive health services.</summary>
